text: Pateros Church, also known as the San Roque Parish Church, is a Roman Catholic church under the order of the Augustinians located in the municipality of Pateros, Metro Manila, Philippines. ==History== Founded after the division of Pateros to Pasig by Fray Andres Vehil. ==Architecture== The plan was created by Fray Santos Gomez Marañon and completed on July 1, 1815, to start the construction.
